      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEEN AVENGER (3) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive three back in her blistering 23.88 win at Bendigo over 425m. Hot win three back and looks the one to beat here. PAW TIFFY (1) has been on speed at the last couple here and fought on to hit the frame, last outing finishing third beaten 5 lengths (23.48). No wins but has five minors at this course. Racing well and deserves a win. FIND THE SUN (4) boasts a consistent overall record including 13 wins from 33 starts, but missed the frame latest when fourth (23.44) over 410m at this track. Form at the trip sound including nine wins. Will go close here with a clear run. FOXY ROXY (2) form at this course and distance reads well.",
